dct_title_s: Rand, McNally & Co.'s indexed atlas of the world map of Japan
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Shows prefectures, cities, mountains, and roads of Japan. Insets: Outline map of Japan -- Ezo and Chisima -- Ryukyu Islands -- South extension of Osumi Province. Index on verso. In upper margin: Rand, McNally & Company's indexed atlas of the world. 538-539. From: Rand, McNally & Co.'s indexed atlas of the world. Chicago, New York : Rand McNally & Co., c1892.
